milestones.description: Steven Outerbridge and Romaine's 90-run partnership is BMUDA's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 75 between David Hemp and Lionel Cann
Ashish Bagai and Abdool Samad's 217-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 106 between John Davison and Ashish Bagai
Canada's 78-run win against Bermuda is the largest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 69-run win against Kenya
Ashish Bagai and Abdool Samad's 217-run partnership is CAN's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 177 between Geoff Barnett and Ian Billcliff

stories.title: Samad ton gives Canada consolation win
stories.subTitle: Canada v Bermuda, 3rd ODI, King City
stories.summary: Abdool Samad slammed his maiden ODI hundred and added 217 runs for the third wicket with Ashish Bagai, who made 84, to star in Canada's 77-run consolation win over Bermuda in the third ODI in King City
